{"id": "art-111", "label": "Art. 111", "title": "Art. 111", "slug": "art-111", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 111 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1567358540\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2344\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1567358540\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Adunarea general&#259; ordinar&#259; se <span\nclass=SpellE>întrune&#351;te</span> cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o\ndat&#259; pe an, în cel mult 5 luni de la încheierea <span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;iului</span>\nfinanciar.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>În afar&#259; de dezbaterea altor probleme înscrise la ordinea de zi,\nadunarea general&#259; este obligat&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1997943639\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2343\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1997943639\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)s&#259; discute, s&#259; aprobe sau s&#259; modifice <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare anuale, pe baza rapoartelor\nprezentate de consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv de directorat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de consiliul de\nsupraveghere, de cenzori sau, dup&#259; caz, de auditorul financiar, <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; fixeze dividendul;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_978462249\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2342\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_978462249\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)s&#259; aleag&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ns&#259; revoce membrii consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv ai consiliului de supraveghere, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncenzorii;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_301839137\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2341\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_301839137\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b<sup>1</sup>)în cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nale c&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ii</span> financiare sunt\nauditate, s&#259; numeasc&#259; sau s&#259; demit&#259; auditorul financiar <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; fixeze durata minim&#259; a contractului de\naudit financiar;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_186249230\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2340\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_186249230\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)s&#259; fixeze <span class=SpellE>remunera&#355;ia</span>\ncuvenit&#259; pentru <span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;iul</span> în curs\nmembrilor consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv membrilor consiliului de supraveghere, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncenzorilor, dac&#259; nu a fost stabilit&#259; prin actul constitutiv;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1737548482\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2339\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1737548482\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)s&#259; se <span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;e</span> asupra\ngestiunii consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv a directoratului;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>e)s&#259;\nstabileasc&#259; bugetul de venituri <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncheltuieli <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dup&#259; caz, programul de\nactivitate, pe <span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;iul</span> financiar\nurm&#259;tor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>f)s&#259;\nhot&#259;rasc&#259; gajarea, închirierea sau <span class=SpellE>desfiin&#355;area</span>\nuneia sau a mai multor <span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;i</span> ale <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>"}